text: The Australian Labor Party is an Australian political party. It is organised into a national organisation as well as a branch in each state and territory, as follows: * Australian Labor Party (New South Wales Branch) (Site) * Australian Labor Party (Victorian Branch) (Site) * Australian Labor Party (Queensland Branch) (Site) * Australian Labor Party (Western Australian Branch) (Site) * Australian Labor Party (South Australian Branch) (Site) * Australian Labor Party (Tasmanian Branch) (Site) * Australian Labor Party (Australian Capital Territory Branch) (Site) * Australian Labor Party (Northern Territory Branch) (Site) * Country Labor is a separate branch for rural and regional areas (Site) ==References==
